      <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Methods and devices to apply adhesive to a collated or gathered stack of sheets for attaching them together, for uniting it with a cover, or both. Usually, the adhesive is applied by a roller, whereby the roller is moved along a stack in a rest position or the stacks are continuously moved along a stationary applicator, as in industrial perfect binders.</paragraph-text>
